modName: MXR Fallout NV Sindragosa character in SKYRIM
summary: A character preset i've made to closely resemble MXR's fallout NV character
descriptionHtml:
INSTALL 
Download mod, extract it just the jslot onto common\Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\Chargen\Presets

THEN WHAT?
Load a save then go showracemenu in console enter the preset tab and then load a preset select the aesa preset and thats it!
author: Masterown1
